sub_title: Chief Executive Officer at Used Products Franchise BV
summary:
Used Products Franchise has over 60 stores. We started in the Netherlands but also opened shops in Belgium, Germany, Romania and Slovenia. We are currently expanding to the rest of Europe. If you are interested in starting your own (master) franchise in Europe, please don't hesitate to contact me.

www.usedproducts.nl

-Bas Hofte
